      <title>渣打银行表示，斯里兰卡准备在五月中旬之前达成债券持有人协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-17/sri-lanka-poised-for-bondholder-deal-by-mid-may-stanchart-says</link>
