      <title>展望缓解对波音交付的担忧，美联航股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/united-airlines-cuts-2024-aircraft-plan-amid-growth-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合航空控股公司(United Airlines Holdings Inc.)预计本季度利润好于预期，该公司股价创下近三个月来最大涨幅，缓解了人们对波音公司飞机延误和监管压力将使扩张计划面临风险的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/united-airlines-cuts-2024-aircraft-plan-amid-growth-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 20:10:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
